{"tid":2495140,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"29單確診有22單乘坐UK6395航班而分別入住三間酒店，好大機會機場檢疫出左問題","createTime":"2021-04-19T04:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T09:10:49.000Z","uid":273218,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"51abda629dbddd983da6bcaad641370ab07f444b","tid":2495140,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210418/N26A2GOCEFAI3JNXYPAGTMLEAA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210418%2FN26A2GOCEFAI3JNXYPAGTMLEAA%2F&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqxzyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=5d446b20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210418%2FN26A2GOCEFAI3JNXYPAGTMLEAA%2F&h=7aa2f579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210418/N26A2GOCEFAI3JNXYPAGTMLEAA/</a><br />\n<br />\n29單確診，有22人同樣乘坐UK6395航班，之後入住三間酒店（赤鱲角富豪機場酒店，西環華美達，北角華美達），所以源頭好大機會唔係酒店而係航班或者出境/轉機機場已經集體感染。<br />\n<br />\n依家機場一定要快速測試陰性先可以入住酒店，好可能出左漏洞。機場除左檢測人員，本身請左大量無謂紙板人搞大龍鳳，但都無阻大量檢測漏洞出現"},{"pid":"16be3bfd754138ea91a3c92a3bbc8424661fe443","tid":2495140,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:46:48.000Z","msg":"機場請咁多紙板人<br />\n（每個單程通道轉彎位都擺一至四個紙板人）<br />\n同請咁多登記人員<br />\n（兩三個櫃檯問重覆問題）<br />\n其實增加感染風險"},{"pid":"f205427464d9b231ed5af9c0eba99aac1e6a565c","tid":2495140,"uid":357031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:04:03.000Z","msg":"幫港共諗好點講：雖然29單確診有22人坐UK6395航班，但無證據顯示係入境檢疫出問題，反而復活節期間大量市民「出行」，增加社區傳播風險，所以需要收緊社交距離措施；另外我哋亦會追究個別傳媒嘅失實報道"},{"pid":"9546515892cbfba4f60b2ff506fdc8cc549d99c8","tid":2495140,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"香港人守得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}